    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced red onion</strong> and cook for 3 min or until softened</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[175ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
