      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>beluga lentils</strong> and<strong> </strong>your <strong>ground cinnamon </strong>and cook for 1 min until everything is combined</p><p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock</strong>,<strong> bay leaf[ves]</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook over a high heat for 3 min or until reduced – this is your <strong>lentil ragù</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
