      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once bubbling and golden, leave the <strong>melty Greek-style lentil moussaka</strong> to cool for 3 min before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Serve the <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>to the side with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and garnish with the <strong>chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch out for the bay leaf[ves] and discard!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
